data.description: Welcome to your mountain retreat. This home boasts a spacious open floor plan with a flag stone Wood fireplace in main living room. Walk out from your living room to a large wrap-around deck with lots of privacy and view of Pikes Peak. Explore the great outdoors with nearby fishing lake and canoeing. Large kitchen with oak cabinets. All appliances included. Large windows upper and lower to enjoy the scenery, birds and wildlife. Walk out lower level with another moss rock wood fireplace. Great investment opportunity whether you are searching for a full-time residence or vacation home. Thanks for showing!!!!
